quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,50,aur hamara hukum to aankhh ke jhapkane ki terhan aik baat hoti hai
  54,51,aur hum tumahray hum mzhbon ko halaak kar chukay hain to koi hai ke soochey samjhay ?
  54,52,"aur jo kuch unhon nekiya, ( un ke ) aamaal naamon mein ( mndrj ) hai"
  54,53,( yani ) har chhota aur bara kaam likh diya gaya hai
  54,54,jo parhaizgaar hain woh baghoon aur nﮦron mein hon ge
  54,55,( yani ) pak maqam mein har terhan ki qudrat rakhnay walay badshah ki bargaah mein
  55,1,( khuda jo ) nihayat meharban
  55,2,isi ne quran ki taleem farmai
  55,3,isi ne ensaan ko pedakiya
  55,4,isi ne is ko bolna sikhaya
  55,5,Sooraj aur chaand aik hisaab muqarrar se chal rahay hain
  55,6,aur bootiyan aur darakht sajda kar rahay hain
  55,7,aur isi ne aasman ko bulandkiya aur traazo qaim ki
  55,8,ke traazo ( se tolnay ) mein hadd se tajawaz nah karo
  55,9,aur insaaf ke sath theek tolo. aur toal kam mat karo
  55,10,aur isi ne khalqat ke liye zameen bichai
  55,11,is mein meway aur khajoor ke darakht hain jin ke khoshon par ghilaaf hotay hain
  55,12,aur anaaj jis ke sath bhus hota hai aur khushbodar phool
  55,13,to ( ae giroh jin o ins ) tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,14,isi ne ensaan kotehkray ki terhan khanlhanti matti se banaya
  55,15,aur jaanat ko aag ke sholay se pedakiya
  55,16,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
